Package: svgedit
Title: Edit SVG files in R to insert ggplot2 plots and text
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
  person(
    "Daniel",
    "Thedie",
    email = "daniel.thedie@ed.ac.uk",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1352-7245")
  )
Description: This package provides functions to edit SVG files created in Inkscape by replacing placeholders (e.g. a rectangle element) by ggplot2 plots or images, and editing text boxes. This automates the creation of figures with complex layouts from R code.
